  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a part of the activation of this jutsu, you must have a weapon in both hands that meet this Bukijutsu' s component requirements.</p><p>You perform a swift series of powerful and accurate strikes with both weapons. Before finishing with a powerful strike with both weapons simultaneously.</p><p>Make two melee Taijutsu attacks, one with each weapon, dealing your [weapons damage] + 1d10. If you scored at least one hit with each weapon, you attack one final time dealing both [weapons damage die] + your Taijutsu ability modifier + 2d10.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d10</p>",
